777
01:24:20,240 --> 01:24:24,153
No, this was preordained long before
either of us were beforn.

778
01:24:24,480 --> 01:24:28,678
It wasn't a doorway that opened, it
was a window that was closing.

779
01:24:28,840 --> 01:24:31,673
