780
01:24:31,800 --> 01:24:36,120
- Stop what?
- The end. Rapture.

781
01:24:36,800 --> 01:24:37,760
Me.

782
01:24:37,800 --> 01:24:42,191
Be careful of a wolf in sheep's clothing.
A man of sin will come at the power of Satan.

783
01:24:42,320 --> 01:24:45,760
He will use all kinds of power, including
miraculous and wonderful signs.

784
01:24:45,840 --> 01:24:48,160
