823
01:27:01,000 --> 01:27:03,673
What if God is real,
and my brother a ... prophet.

824
01:27:05,320 --> 01:27:06,840
We all must make sacrifices.

825
01:27:06,920 --> 01:27:10,400
What will your sacrifice to God be?

826
01:27:12,560 --> 01:27:16,400
Who are you?
What are you?

827
01:27:18,720 --> 01:27:20,520
I am the end.

828
01:27:44,440 --> 01:27:47,477
<i>To those of you who don't know me, I'm Joseph Crone.</i>

829
01:27:47,600 --> 01:27:52,276
<i>And to those of you who do, my loyal readers
around the world, millions of you,</i>

830
01:27:52,400 --> 01:27:54,480
<i>made my books bestsellers.</i>

831
01:27:56,680 --> 01:27:58,760
<i>I have something very important
to tell you all.</i>

832
01:28:02,320 --> 01:28:05,200
<i>For years I criticized religion.</i>

833
01:28:05,600 --> 01:28:09,912
<i>I rejected the existence of God.
