834
01:28:10,040 --> 01:28:11,598
<i>I've been awakened</i>

835
01:28:11,720 --> 01:28:15,679
<i>And I can tell you beyond a shadow of a doubt,
that not only does God exists,</i>

836
01:28:15,800 --> 01:28:20,351
<i>but my brother, Samuel, is one of his chosen ones.</i>

837
01:28:20,480 --> 01:28:24,519
<i>He's a savior, he's a saint, a messenger.</i>

838
